{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Although various secure transmission schemes such as artificial noise, beamforming, and cooperative jamming have been proposed, they are highly dependent on perfect CSI [271].",
    "AI-based secure transmission schemes can overcome this limitation, enabling dynamic and heterogeneous ISAC systems.Liu et al. [248] proposed a secure transmission scheme for the IRS-assisted ISAC system, where the sensing target acted as an eavesdropper and artificial noise was injected to confuse it.",
    "The authors maximized the secrecy rate by jointly optimizing the transmit beamforming, the artificial noise matrix, and the IRS phase shift.",
    "A DRL-based algorithm was developed to deal with this non-convex problem with the coupled variables.",
    "Zhu et al. [249] investigated long-term secure transmission for the simultaneously transmitting and reflecting IRS-supported ISAC networks."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Although various secure transmission schemes such as artificial noise, beamforming, and cooperative jamming have been proposed, they are highly dependent on perfect CSI [271].",
